data.description: Southbay newer San Diego home, a gem of tranquility and convenience.  This spacious 5-bedroom, 3-bath beautifully maintained home, constructed in the year 2000, offers the perfect blend of modern living and timeless beauty.  As you step onto this home, you'll be greeted by a meticulously landscaped yard adorned with mature fruit-bearing trees in the backyard, alkaline water flirtation system in entire home, creating an oasis of natural beauty and serenity.
